{quote}we need to ignore subtasks (maybe epics?){quote}

Let’s ignore {{subtasks}} but not {{epics}}. This is to match Jira behavior on {{sprint reports}}

{quote}what to do with “issues completed outside of this sprint”?{quote}

Let’s ignore “issues completed outside of sprint”. In future, we will create a separate widget to track {{points completed outside of sprint}}.



